import React from "react";
import { UserPhotoContainer } from "../userIcon/userIcon.style";
import {
  SearchContainer,
  SearchButtonContainer,
  SearchInputContainer,
} from "./Search.style";

const Search = () => {
  return (
    <SearchContainer>
      <SearchInputContainer
        class="searchInput"
        type="text"
        name=""
        placeholder="Search"
      />
      <SearchButtonContainer>
        <UserPhotoContainer>
          <svg
            width="79"
            height="78"
            viewBox="0 0 79 78"
            fill="none"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          >
            <circle cx="54" cy="25" r="23" stroke="black" stroke-width="4" />
            <line
              x1="37.0904"
              y1="41.1518"
              x2="2.09036"
              y2="75.1518"
              stroke="black"
              stroke-width="6"
            />
          </svg>
        </UserPhotoContainer>
      </SearchButtonContainer>
    </SearchContainer>
  );
};
export default Search;
